{
  "stem": "1491.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't recall it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall if we walked or they took us by trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plaszow was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It only was missing the crematoriums, the ovens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, was hell on earth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's very hard to describe it, even.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All of it, the Germans with the dogs, and here is killing, there is killing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You really-- you didn't know if you were coming or going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that time when we came to Plaszow, it just happened they had a transport going, for men, to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Wagons were waiting for men to ship them to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they took our men, put them on the wagons to Mauthausen, which they never made Brnenec, because everybody knew Brnenec was going to be good, going to save your life.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was so hot, and they had no water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember I was running towards the wagons to see him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And like you see in the Spielberg where he hoses down all those wagons with water, with cold water, this was that transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Schindler came down to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- like in the movie, he shows, let's get them wet for a joke.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this cold water helped them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was such a heat that it helped them a little bit in those wagons.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
